@gerdegotit sounds like such an awesome memory. I loved trampolines as a kid, one of my favorite things growing up
Big smile across my face all the way through, beautiful work
@1959do Jon Brion phone call I believe it’s on the eternal sunshine of the spotless mind soundtrack, my fav song ❤️

This is such a relaxing video to watch!
Wow, that's such a great short story ❤️
Save water 💦💦 To day World water day 💫💦💫✨💦❤️
@dimple224 it's a feature on my samsung
